{"tid":663202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"知道左老公偷食，比左頂綠帽佢帶","createTime":"2018-05-13T05:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T06:30:36.000Z","uid":5770,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75857698e01514bc35011218c2c011b61c7895ed","tid":663202,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"我16歲同佢拍拖，老公大我10年，而家我都二十出頭，老公竟然同個後生女開房，睇相大約18-20歲。<br />\n我發現左老公偷食個晚，我好唔開心，一個人慢無目的咁周圍行，咁岩墥到一個舊同學，佢見我好唔開心，就話不如陪我飲酒，忘記哂所有唔開心既野。如是者，我就飲醉左，到左第二日起身，我先發現同佢發生左關係。佢話我琴晚攬住佢，唔比佢走。<br />\n個件事之後，佢經常想約我，仲話如果老公唔要我，佢會要我。<br />\n過左個半月後，我懷疑自己有左，跟住去驗孕，證實左有左bb，而家我都唔知點算好。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a9652c0060219f6fdb535158d2ded2e97f4f7b","tid":663202,"uid":52221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"男人都可以有bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fe1bfe526130a6ae3be18e6adab0471ac3fcea","tid":663202,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"男的也會懷孕？"},{"pid":"740896b47010061b2f013c8578b28ff95cf389ba","tid":663202,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"唔起底都知係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb104c74ef363f02f3bcceb5f30b51b9f7653c","tid":663202,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a9652c0060219f6fdb535158d2ded2e97f4f7b","tid":663202,"uid":52221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"男人都可以有bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:20: